# Build context is the monorepo root for every service image. Keep it lean:
# node_modules is reinstalled inside the image, and build artifacts / local
# state must never leak into a layer.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.output
**/.nitro
**/.tanstack
**/.vercel
.demo
.git
.github
.agents
.claude
*.log
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
**/.DS_Store
coverage
# Docs and specs are not needed at build/runtime.
*.md
!README.md
